{"tid":970574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[臭🐥同學會?] 被網友討論「幾錢一晚」　朱智賢：我唔係做開","createTime":"2019-01-06T03:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T16:54:45.000Z","uid":12558,"like":12,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"253c47bd9a70f9baef6ff0826d43cf13c78625e5","tid":970574,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:00:38.000Z","msg":"最新一集《後生仔傾吓偈》以「做藝人係未要面皮夠厚？」為題，仲搵嚟朱智賢、胡鴻鈞、劉佩玥、黃庭鋒做嘉賓，朱智賢話自己暫時都未遇過好攻擊性嘅負評，最多都係被指年紀大，但提到最想反擊嘅留言時，佢就話試過喺討論區見到「幾錢一晚」嘅題目，令佢十分之嬲，對於女藝人被問價一事，6號認為時有發生，但朱智賢聽到6號嗰句「好常見」後，反應十分之大，「咩好多女星都有？我唔係做開呢啲嘢架嘛！佢哋好似已經assume我係做呢樣嘢！」朱智賢表示每次見到類似嘅留言，都極有衝動想留言為自己澄清。<br />\n<br />\n見到朱智賢咁激動，<span style=\"color: red;\">馮盈盈插咀表示:「我知道點解嬲，佢係未開得太平？試過有人inbox問我五百蚊過夜得唔得？」</span>FYY此言一出，全場人都笑到收唔到聲，連本身好嬲嘅朱智賢都認唔住爆出一句「我無咁低價。」對於被出價五百元一事，FYY有感不被尊重，所以即時將對方封鎖。而朱智賢亦都「呼籲」有意問價的話，不妨直接當面問，在旁嘅胡鴻鈞反應都幾快，即問「幾錢晚？」朱智賢就好霸氣咁回覆：「幾錢都唔得！」其實講到負評，FYY近年都有唔少，佢話最介意係被指「cheap」、「上唔到大場面」，更笑言自己本身好優雅，只係為咗同觀眾拉近距離，所以將自己降級。真係辛苦晒喎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tb9N5uL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTb9N5uL.png&h=3f49b16d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPAtPWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPAtPWr.png&h=8b47a15f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5WXJgr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5WXJgr.png&h=0d6b33b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMMEb9N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMMEb9N.png&h=0f42ada4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SYSw9N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SYSw9N.png&h=a14a6519&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P38Wen8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP38Wen8.png&h=037ca32d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPxoDPO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPxoDPO.png&h=ed254170&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXHPzn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXHPzn9.png&h=9e0a0fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdDGquP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdDGquP.png&h=7c31244b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6638b537645d1eb7bddb7dc47c544d5dfe1ffcd0","tid":970574,"uid":132587,"like":332,"dislike":3,"score":329,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"唔係做開即係有做"},{"pid":"a806eb7242f19e3873455fa856b1de269da2181d","tid":970574,"uid":51041,"like":9,"dislike":16,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"條女真係好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be288f406db3abb3cbeb4df38c2bf41865f70400","tid":970574,"uid":59617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1208bca4fa209ba32e8d60f31bf69df850f617ac","tid":970574,"uid":23400,"like":16,"dislike":7,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:09:28.000Z","msg":"莊思敏表示十萬都唔夠佢買隻錶呀，出到出高D啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9e1589e3f384ce3d93737b481eb2d0da705d46","tid":970574,"uid":37733,"like":261,"dislike":2,"score":259,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"朱智賢都認唔住爆出一句「我無咁低價。」<br />\n即係高價就可以?"},{"pid":"b95c4358f68f96942a0329fdcfd45c080a3799cc","tid":970574,"uid":71144,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"好似連登仔咁問<br />\n開價100萬1Q制唔制<br />\n睇佢哋點應機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e8afc0df9ed769d34d55